# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:14
translate chinese rebas2_cff9d76e:

    # rb "I thought I already told you about my job?"
    rb "我以为我已经跟你说过我的工作了？"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:15
translate chinese rebas2_b942330d:

    # rb "Yeah, I work at Midnight Mechanics in town."
    rb "是啊，我在镇上的“午夜修车行”工作。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:16
translate chinese rebas2_3726a81f:

    # rb "I'm the best mechanic in that place."
    rb "我是那儿最棒的修车师傅。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:18
translate chinese rebas2_27b60394:

    # rb "And I love it. Love cars - fixing them, building them, driving them."
    rb "而且我热爱这份工作。热爱汽车——修理它们、改装它们、驾驶它们。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:19
translate chinese rebas2_35359c22:

    # rb "Just love it all."
    rb "这一切我都爱。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:20
translate chinese rebas2_2773121f:

    # pc "That's cool that you love your job."
    pc "你热爱自己的工作，真棒。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:22
translate chinese rebas2_fca00824:

    # rb "I wouldn't go that far."
    rb "我倒没那么夸张。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:23
translate chinese rebas2_ed492ac7:

    # rb "I love working on the cars, but dealing with all the people isn't nearly as fun."
    rb "我喜欢修车，但应付那些人可没那么有趣。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:24
translate chinese rebas2_8cae6e54:

    # rb "I really want to go to school. I want to learn more, get into a full career."
    rb "我真的很想上学。我想学更多东西，走上正经的职业道路。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:26
translate chinese rebas2_e9b9036d:

    # rb "But you've seen how Mama gets when I mention college."
    rb "但你见过我一提大学，妈妈会是什么反应。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:27
translate chinese rebas2_d7ff2343:

    # pc "You should do what makes you happy though, not worry about what your mother might think about it."
    pc "不过你应该做让自己开心的事，别担心你妈妈会怎么想。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:28
translate chinese rebas2_f04f4439:

    # rb "Yeah, I know."
    rb "是啊，我知道。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:29
translate chinese rebas2_2c936330:

    # rb "But I do care what she thinks. I do want to make her happy."
    rb "但我确实很在意她的想法。我确实想让她开心。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:30
translate chinese rebas2_b11bdd65:

    # rb "Even if I know that she's wrong about so many things, I still love her and want her to be proud of me."
    rb "即使我知道她在很多事情上都错了，但我依然爱她，希望她为我感到骄傲。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:31
translate chinese rebas2_f4d99595:

    # pc "I understand. It's more important to be proud of yourself though."
    pc "我理解。不过，为自己感到骄傲更重要。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:32
translate chinese rebas2_c113f718:

    # pc "Don't hold yourself back just to make your mother happy."
    pc "别为了取悦你妈妈而束缚自己。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:34
translate chinese rebas2_9a718c35:

    # rb "Thanks, [pcname]. You're right."
    rb "谢谢，[pcname]。你说得对。"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebas2.rpy:35
translate chinese rebas2_f2ae53f4:

    # rb "Something to think about."
    rb "值得思考的问题。"

